Name: Accounting Basics Explained Through a Story
Description: New to Accounting? In this video I will introduce you to the world of accounting by telling you a story. This quick tutorial gives you an introduction to accounting and explains the concepts of income statement (Profit & Loss) - balance sheet and the accounting equation (Assets = Liabilities + Equity).
